com.vmware.nsx_policy.infra.segments

Class SegmentsFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vmware.nsx_policy.infra.segments.SegmentsFactory

  • public class SegmentsFactory
extends Object
    SegmentsFactory is responsible for creating instances of services contained inside the com.vmware.nsx_policy.infra.segments package and also has the subpackages reference to access respective subpackage services.
